PrecisAmendments to the GOVERNMENT AIRPORT CONCESSION OPERATIONS REGULATIONS that authorize the manager of a non-designated airport to issue licences authorizing people who operate a passenger-carrying business (taxicabs, limousines, courtesy vehicles) from a location other than the airport to pick up customers who have made advance arrangements with them.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1996-0088 Publication Date: 1996-02-07
Attachments
precis:
Amendments to the GOVERNMENT AIRPORT CONCESSION OPERATIONS REGULATIONS that
authorize the manager of a non-designated airport to issue licences
authorizing people who operate a passenger-carrying business (taxicabs,
limousines, courtesy vehicles) from a location other than the airport to
pick up customers who have made advance arrangements with them.
